1.title: The Oh My Disney Show Vol.1 with Joey Bragg

episode of.title: The Oh My Disney Show (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Join our hosts as they talk all-things Disney including an exclusive clip debut from Beauty and the Beast, Auli'i Cravalho from Moana, and Baymax charades. Plus, Toy Story Skydiving, and Liv and Maddie's Joey Bragg.

2.title: In A Tale As Old As Time: Beauty and the Beast

episode of.title: The Oh My Disney Show (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: Today on The Oh My Disney Show, Josh Gad and Luke Evans at the Beauty and the Beast press junket. Plus, everything live-action Beauty and the Beast including the gray stuff.

4.title: With Marvel's Stan Lee

episode of.title: The Oh My Disney Show (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: This week on The Oh My Disney Show we have special guests Stan Lee, and Ethan Craft from Disney Channels Lizzie McGuire. Also, we're playing a new exciting game, the Mulan Challenge.

5.title: With Chris Pratt Always, Forever In Your Mind

episode of.title: The Oh My Disney Show (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: Tour Walt Disney Studio's lot, find out what Chris Pratt and the Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2 cast think their characters' favorite emoji would be, get a rare tour of the Castle Suite at Cinderella Castle in Walt Disney World, and watch Forever in Your Mind perform "Smooth".

imdb.plot outline: Oh My Disney represents a unique opportunity for Disney to re-tell our classic stories in a voice that speaks directly to you. We deliver original and shareable content about classic and current Disney characters to fans through a variety of videos, GIFs, trivia, and quippy editorial.
